  "title": "CIVIL & STRUCTURAL ENGINEER",
  "description": "<p><strong>Civil &amp; Structural Engineer</strong></p>\n<p><strong>(Construction sector)</strong></p>\n<p>Responsibilities:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Report to Project/Construction Manager</li>\n  <li>Assist Project/Construction Manager to plan &amp; execute structural &amp;      architectural works.</li>\n  <li>Site supervision &amp; coordinate with client, architect, consultant &amp; RE/RTO etc.</li>\n  <li>Manage direct work force.</li>\n  <li>Coordinate inspections of civil and structural works.</li>\n  <li>Monitor project schedule and progress.</li>\n  <li>Contract administration, other site operational &amp; project management matters</li>\n  <li>All matters on site in relation to the duties &amp; responsibilities of a C&amp;S      Engineer</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Recognized bachelor’s degree in civil engineering or equivalent.</li>\n  <li>Minimum 2 years of relevant work experience in construction trade in Singapore such as HDB newbuild/BTO/D&amp;B project etc.</li>\n  <li>Preferred Singaporean to apply.</li>\n</ul>",
